author: dims
msg: Fix for Bug 12853 - ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException caused by utils.bytecode
- Remove the cache from ParamNameExtractor as it is NEVER cleaned up.
- ParamNameExtractor is now stateless, so there should not be problems caused by multiple threads...
- Add a cache to ServiceDesc itself
- Add a synchronized block around this cache.
- Since the cache is in ServiceDesc, it should theoretically get cleaned up when this ServiceDesc goes out of scope...
